            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "軟銀股價上漲，據報導其重啟100億美元OpenAI抵押貸款談判",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NfZ7.qMBBDB7.JTTWKvvyg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC6H01W_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 軟銀集團股價週四上漲，此前<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"路透社\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:路透社;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/路透社\">路透社</a>報導稱，這家日本科技投資巨頭已重啟一項以其OpenAI持股為抵押、規模達100億美元的貸款談判，旨在為其積極進取的人工智能投資策略提供資金支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">軟銀集團（TYO:9984）股價上漲2.3%，報¥6,137，表現優於日本大盤，同期日經225指數僅上漲約0.5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據路透社報導，由於銀行方面不願僅以這家非上市的ChatGPT開發商的股份作為唯一抵押品，此前談判一度陷入僵局。如今，軟銀已重返與銀行財團的磋商桌。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9ed56380-02ba-3a05-becb-31feca51836b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為消除貸款方的顧慮，路透社報導稱，軟銀現已提出提供企業擔保，若所抵押的OpenAI股份不足以償還貸款，貸款方可向軟銀公司追討還款。據報導，高盛、摩根大通及瑞穗金融集團預計將參與此次貸款財團。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次擬議的保證金貸款，是軟銀創辦人孫正義大力擴展集團人工智能版圖這一宏觀戰略的組成部分。路透社稱，軟銀已向OpenAI及相關人工智能基礎設施項目承諾投入逾600億美元，其中包括Stargate數據中心合資項目，並日益依賴債務融資及資產抵押融資來支撐上述投資。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">路透社指出，由於非上市公司股份較上市股票更難估值和變現，貸款方對以此類資產作抵押的貸款態度趨於審慎。報導稱，軟銀此前在遭遇潛在貸款方的抵制後，已下調了融資目標規模。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">路透社補充稱，OpenAI上月已秘密提交美國首次公開募股（IPO）申請，若其最終成功上市，將有助於提升該投資的估值透明度，並可能進一步增強其作為抵押品的實用價值。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>報導：Roushni Nair</em></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BB%9F%E9%8A%80%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E%E5%85%B6%E9%87%8D%E5%95%9F100%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83openai%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%BC%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4-034723251.html",
