        {
            "title": "澳洲5月貿易意外錄得逆差，進口大幅攀升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ybj6lTjOjCGK3QZKLbwmcQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC290VC_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 澳洲5月貿易數據出乎市場預料，進口急劇上升，增速超越出口增長，導致貿易帳由順差轉為逆差，反映出在內需保持韌性的背景下，貿易格局正在發生轉變。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳洲5月貿易差額錄得30.2億澳元（21億美元）逆差，而4月份修訂後數據為13.8億澳元順差，遠遜於經濟學家預期的21.9億澳元順差。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">出口方面，5月按月增長6.9%，4月修訂後增幅為7.2%。出口增長主要受大宗商品及農產品出貨量上升帶動，亦得益於亞洲主要市場的穩定需求支撐。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a6be33f3-47d6-33f9-abf9-fbe2f06239b3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">進口方面，5月按月上升2.6%，較4月的0.2%明顯加速，反映資本設備、消費品及工業原料的採購需求有所增強。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一意外逆差或對市場對澳洲第二季經濟增長的預期造成壓力，此前外部板塊在近幾個季度一直為整體經濟提供支撐。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次數據公布之際，投資者正密切評估澳洲經濟前景及澳洲儲備銀行的貨幣政策走向。澳洲儲備銀行目前對宣告通脹壓力得到控制仍持審慎態度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B25%E6%9C%88%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E9%8C%84%E5%BE%97%E9%80%86%E5%B7%AE-%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E6%94%80%E5%8D%87-025130051.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 10:57:17",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "亞洲芯片股下挫，OpenAI效率提升及Meta雲端計劃報道引發拋售",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GQcDb8ntU.u8og0ujZxDlw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAB20CL_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com — 亞洲半導體股週四普遍下跌，此前美國芯片股隔夜遭遇大幅拋售。據報道，OpenAI在運行人工智能模型方面取得了顯著的效率提升，同時Meta Platforms Inc（納斯達克：META）也正在探索將多餘AI運算能力變現的方式。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據科技媒體The Information報道，OpenAI工程師開發出一套軟件優化方案，能夠將推理成本削減約一半，從而減少為部分ChatGPT用戶提供服務所需的英偉達顯示卡數量，此消息令市場情緒明顯受挫。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dd36a7ac-6879-3655-97ec-3fe471a395ff-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一進展引發市場憂慮，未來AI芯片的需求增長或將低於此前預期。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">韓國兩大芯片巨頭三星電子（KS:005930）及SK海力士（KS:000660）股價均大幅下挫，跌幅介於8%至10%之間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本愛德萬測試（TYO:6857）股價跌逾7%，東京電子（TYO:8035）股價亦下跌約5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在中國台灣上市的台積電（TW:2330）股價跌幅逾2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雪上加霜的是，彭博新聞報道指出，Meta Platforms正在開發雲端業務，計劃出售多餘的AI運算能力，此舉旨在從其龐大的AI基礎設施投資中獲取回報。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週三的報道顯示，Meta正考慮通過一項新的雲端服務，向客戶提供AI模型及閒置運算能力的使用權。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述兩項進展同時引發市場擔憂——AI企業或許能夠從現有硬件中挖掘出更多價值，從而降低採購新芯片的迫切性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%8A%AF%E7%89%87%E8%82%A1%E4%B8%8B%E6%8C%AB-openai%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E5%8F%8Ameta%E9%9B%B2%E7%AB%AF%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E6%8B%8B%E5%94%AE-023238711.html",
